2- public static EmployeeBuilder builder()
        explain
            1- I using builder design to write clean code.
            2- You can used this function to easy create object or new employee in database
            3- How can i using this function
                1- Write the class name like Employee before write the object name after the object name write =
                2- After = write the class name after that write .builder()
                3- After that you can set the attributes like .id(12).name("Ahmed")
                4- After finishing set all attributes must be write .build();
            4- example
                Employee employee = Employee.builder()
                            .name("Ahmed")
                            .gender(true)
                            .birthdate(new Date())
                            .salary(2020d)
                            .build();
